headline.main: VICHY RULING SAVES 2 MORE SPANIARDS; Extradition Denied -- Former Premier Interned for Safety

lead_paragraph: VICHY, France, Nov. 21 -- Francisco Largo Caballero, exiled Spanish republican former Premier, has been administratively interned at Vals-les-Bains, it was learned here today following the rejection by the Limoges tribunal of the Spanish Government's request for his extradition.
abstract: Algiers ct grants Spanish extradition claim against M Roderiguez Martinez, former Mayor of Elche
